# 下面开始技术总结
Next is our cooking tips:
第一，	切猪肝之前必须清洗干净，切好之后不用冲洗，
First, rinse and clean the pork liver well before cutting it. No more washing or rinsing is further needed, in order to have the best flavor.
这样才能爆出猪肝原香味（建议此做法切好之后不清洗）
第二，	腌制猪肝的时候不必加入淀粉，只需要盐胡椒粉老抽即可
Second, no need for any corn starch.  Only need salt, white pepper powder, and dark soy sauce.
第三，	此版本为家常做法，湖南地区可以加入适量的豆豉增加地方风味
Third, you can add fermented soybean if you prefer HuNan cuisine.
小炒猪肝的技术总结完毕
That concludes the tips for Stir-Fried Pork Liver.
